    <item>
      <title>美联储做出了正确的利率决定：摩根大通的米歇尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/fed-made-the-right-rate-decision-jpmorgan-s-michele-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司全球固定收益主管鲍勃·米歇尔 (Bob Michele) 表示，他对美联储的利率决定“感到惊喜”。他在“彭博监测：美联储决定”节目中发言。美联储连续第三次下调基准利率，但减少了 2025 年预期降息次数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/fed-made-the-right-rate-decision-jpmorgan-s-michele-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 19:35:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息25个基点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/fed-cuts-interest-rates-by-25-basis-points-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储将基准利率下调 25 个基点至 4.25%-4.5% 区间。这是美联储连续第三次降息。政策制定者还减少了 2025 年预期降息次数。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/fed-cuts-interest-rates-by-25-basis-points-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 19:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
